1 contributoralbums i’ve listened to 2023 lyricsthese are albums that i listened to and reviewed over the course of 2023

a lot of these especially around the beginning are shitpost albums which ive listened to mostly as a joke

a lot of these people can be easily contacted so if there’s any reason you want to reach out to them please dont as i wouldnt want them to get unwanted attention this is just a list

i’d also like to say that i am listening to these as albums i do not condone the acts andor share the beliefs of artists whose reputations are not good

some of these albums are new additions to my record collection which can be seen on a different list on genius that i wrote
